### ============================================================
### 길드 채팅 APIs (chatservice)
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 전송
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-User-Nickname: TestUser
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello everyone!"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 최신 메시지 조회 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 새 메시지 조회 (폴링)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/new?since=2025-01-15T10:00:00
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 ID 이후 메시지 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/after/100
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 이전 메시지 조회 (무한 스크롤)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/before/100?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 검색
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/search?keyword=hello&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 채팅방 정보 조회 (참여자 수, 안읽은 메시지 수)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/info
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 조회 (안읽은 수 포함)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/with-unread?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 읽음 처리
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/read/100
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 채팅방 입장
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/join
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-User-Nickname: TestUser
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 채팅방 퇴장
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-User-Nickname: TestUser
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 채팅방 참여 상태 확인
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/participation-status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 현재 채팅방 참여자 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/chat/participants
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
